      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。我先确认一下结构：main分支先有ZERO提交，然后分出develop分支做A提交。develop后续还要再分featureA分支，对吧？另外cherry-pick具体要拿哪些提交？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "main",
        "develop",
        "ZERO",
        "A",
        "featureA"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，develop分出featureA。cherry-pick的场景是：main在ONE、TWO之后，需要把develop上的A提交cherry-pick过去；然后在THREE之后，再把featureA上的FIX提交cherry-pick到main。这是典型的PLC热修复场景。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ONE",
        "TWO",
        "THREE",
        "A",
        "FIX",
        "cherry-pick"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我来画一下。main分支：ZERO → ONE → TWO → cherry-pick A → THREE → cherry-pick FIX。develop分支：从ZERO分出，有A → B → C，中间checkout回main做ONE，然后再回develop继续。featureA从develop分出，做FIX → FIX-2。最后develop还要merge featureA。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "main",
        "develop",
        "featureA",
        "ZERO",
        "ONE",
        "TWO",
        "THREE",
        "A",
        "B",
