        "FIX-2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，develop上的B提交是在什么时候？是在checkout到main做ONE之前还是之后？还有featureA的FIX-2需要被cherry-pick吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "develop",
        "B",
        "ONE",
        "FIX-2",
        "cherry-pick"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "B是在checkout main做ONE之后，回到develop才提交的。featureA的FIX-2不需要cherry-pick到main，只有FIX需要。FIX-2留在featureA里，最后通过merge进develop就行。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "B",
