      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "图的方向用LR（从左到右）吧，这样分支走向更清晰。另外标题定为\"Three branches and a cherry-pick from each (IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic)\"，突出这是工业PLC逻辑的特定场景。",
